{"id":924,"parent_id":921,"book_id":1,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":924,"title":"Jonah 3","subtitle":"","short_title":"Jonah","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jonah/3","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Chapter 3"],[".studySummary",["i","Jonah prophesies the downfall of Nineveh—The people repent, and the city is saved."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jonah/3.1","order":"02.33.003.61739"},["b","1"],"And the word of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"came unto Jonah the second time, saying,"],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jonah/3.2","order":"02.33.003.61740"},["b","2"],"Arise, go unto Nineveh, that great city, and",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_2a"},"preach"],"unto it the preaching that I bid thee."],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jonah/3.3","order":"02.33.003.61741"},["b","3"],"So Jonah arose, and went unto Nineveh, according to the word of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],". Now Nineveh was an",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_3a"},"exceeding great city"],"of three days’",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_3b"},"journey"],"."],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jonah/3.4","order":"02.33.003.61742"},["b","4"],"And Jonah began to enter into the city a day’s journey, and he cried, and said, Yet forty days, and Nineveh shall be overthrown."],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jonah/3.5","order":"02.33.003.61743"},["b","5"],"¶",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_5a"},"So"],"the people of",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_5b"},"Nineveh"],"believed God, and proclaimed a",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_5c"},"fast"],", and put on sackcloth, from the greatest of them even to the least of them."],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jonah/3.6","order":"02.33.003.61744"},["b","6"],"For word came unto the king of Nineveh, and he arose from his throne, and he laid his robe from him, and covered",["i","him"],"with",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_6a"},"sackcloth"],", and sat in ashes."],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jonah/3.7","order":"02.33.003.61745"},["b","7"],"And he caused",["i","it"],"to be proclaimed and published through Nineveh by the decree of the king and his nobles, saying, Let neither man nor beast, herd nor flock, taste any thing: let them not feed, nor drink water:"],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jonah/3.8","order":"02.33.003.61746"},["b","8"],"But let man and beast be covered with sackcloth, and cry mightily unto God: yea, let them",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_8a"},"turn"],"every one from his evil way, and from the violence that",["i","is"],"in their hands."],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jonah/3.9","order":"02.33.003.61747"},["b","9"],"Who can tell",["i","if"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_9a"},"God"],"will turn and repent, and turn away from his fierce anger, that we perish not?"],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jonah/3.10","order":"02.33.003.61748"},["b","10"],"¶And God",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_10a"},"saw"],"their works, that they",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_10b"},"turned"],"from their",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_10c"},"evil"],"way; and God repented of the evil, that he had said that he would do unto them; and he did",["i","it"],["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_10d"},"not"],"."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"2a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jonah/3.2a","order":"02.33.003.61749"},["b","2a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/missionary-work"},"TG Missionary Work"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/preaching"},"Preaching"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/prophets-mission-of"},"Prophets, Mission of"],"."],["div",{"id":"3a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jonah/3.3a","order":"02.33.003.61751"},["b","3a"],["span.small","HEB"],"great city to God."],["div",{"id":"3b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jonah/3.3b","order":"02.33.003.61753"},["b","3b"],["span.small","IE"],"through greater Nineveh with its environs."],["div",{"id":"5a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jonah/3.5a","order":"02.33.003.61755"},["b","5a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/31.5"},"Alma 31:5"],"."],["div",{"id":"5b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jonah/3.5b","order":"02.33.003.61757"},["b","5b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/matt/12.41"},"Matt. 12:41"],"."],["div",{"id":"5c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jonah/3.5c","order":"02.33.003.61759"},["b","5c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/fast-fasting"},"TG Fast, Fasting"],"."],["div",{"id":"6a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jonah/3.6a","order":"02.33.003.61761"},["b","6a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/11.25"},"Mosiah 11:25"],"."],["div",{"id":"8a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jonah/3.8a","order":"02.33.003.61763"},["b","8a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/19.33"},"Alma 19:33"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/20.26"},"3 Ne. 20:26"],"."],["div",{"id":"9a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jonah/3.9a","order":"02.33.003.61765"},["b","9a"],["span.small","JST"],"Jonah 3:9 …",["i","we"],"will repent, and",["i","turn unto God, but he will"],"turn away from",["i","us"],"his fierce anger …"],["div",{"id":"10a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jonah/3.10a","order":"02.33.003.61767"},["b","10a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/121.24"},"D&C 121:24"],"."],["div",{"id":"10b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jonah/3.10b","order":"02.33.003.61769"},["b","10b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/repent"},"TG Repent"],"."],["div",{"id":"10c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jonah/3.10c","order":"02.33.003.61771"},["b","10c"],["span.small","JST"],"Jonah 3:10 … evil way",["i","and repented;"],"and God",["i","turned away"],"the evil that he had said he would",["i","bring upon them."]],["div",{"id":"10d","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jonah/3.10d","order":"02.33.003.61773"},["b","10d"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/56.4.4-6"},"D&C 56:4 (4–6)"],"."]]}
